If you will stumble upon any issues with the Ninja configure of the CMake, do the following:

```bash
rm -rf build
cmake -S . -B build -G Ninja
cmake --build build
```

After than we need to check whether everything is fine. Run the following:

```bash
cmake -S . -B build -G Ninja
cmake --build build
find build -maxdepth 2 -type f
```